data.description: Step into this delightful home and be greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere. The well-designed layout maximizes the use of space, ensuring a comfortable living experience. This is an ideal space for those seeking a cozy and efficient lifestyle. This home is comepletely updated within the last 10 years with soft close cabinets, renovated bathroom, and a large deck with fully grown bushes that provide all the privacy you would need. House is fully fenced and has a great storage shed for all your tools and equipment. Situated in central Mandan, this home offers easy access to a variety of amenities and services. Enjoy the convenience of nearby shops, restaurants, parks, and more, all within a short distance from your doorstep. Whether you are a first-time buyer or looking to downsize, this 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom home in central Mandan provides the perfect opportunity for comfortable and convenient living.
